indexPattern.name: indexPattern
indexPattern.description: Go to a specific pattern in the 'palette'. If the index is <= 1, the first pattern will be selected, if it is >= nPatterns, the last pattern will be selected

nextPattern.name: nextPattern
nextPattern.description: Go to next pattern in 'palette'. If reached end of palette, go back to pattern 0. Must be > 0

prevPattern.name: prevPattern
prevPattern.description: Go to previous pattern in 'palette'. If reached pattern 0, go to last pattern in palette. Must be > 0

transportToStart.name: transportToStart
transportToStart.description: Set this object to anything other than 0 to go to first frame of currently selected sequence/playlist (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportJogBack.name: transportJogBack
transportJogBack.description: Set this object to anything other than 0 to go to the previous frame of currently selected sequence/playlist (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportPlayReverse.name: transportPlayReverse
transportPlayReverse.description: Determine whether the currently selected pattern/playlist is playing in reverse (if the currently selected pattern is not a sequence/playlist, this value will return 0). You can set this value to anything other than 0 to play the currently selected sequence/playlist in reverse (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportStop.name: transportStop
transportStop.description: Determine whether the currently selected pattern/playlist is stopped (if the currently selected pattern is not a sequence/playlist, this value will return 0). You can set this value to anything other than 0 to play the currently selected sequence/playlist in reverse (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportPlayForward.name: transportPlayForward
transportPlayForward.description: Determine whether the currently selected pattern/playlist is playing forward (if the currently selected pattern is not a sequence/playlist, this value will return 0). You can set this value to anything other than 0 to play the currently selected sequence/playlist forward (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportJogNext.name: transportJogNext
transportJogNext.description: Set this object to anything other than 0 to go to the next frame of currently selected sequence/playlist (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportToEnd.name: transportToEnd
transportToEnd.description: Set this object to anything other than 0 to go to the last frame of currently selected sequence/playlist (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).

transportLoop.name: transportLoop
transportLoop.description: Determine whether the currently selected pattern/playlist is looped (if the currently selected pattern is not a sequence/playlist, this value will return 0). You can set this value to 0 to disable loop, or anything other than 0 to loop the currently selected sequence/playlist (this will have no effect if a non-sequence pattern is selected in the configuration).
